ip-developer-beijing?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平在今年第一次政治局学习会上推动“颠覆性创新”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3250612/chinas-xi-jinping-pushes-disruptive-innovation-first-politburo-study-session-year?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在中共最高决策机构会议上，习近平表示，中国必须“打好核心技术攻坚战”，增强供应链应对美国遏制的韧性。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 12:04:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3250612/chinas-xi-jinping-pushes-disruptive-innovation-first-politburo-study-session-year?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国高级外交官王毅与赵太烈首次通电话，表示中国愿意与韩国保持联系</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3250609/china-willing-keep-touch-south-korea-first-phone-call-between-top-diplomats-wang-yi-cho-tae-yul?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>赵太烈就任韩国外相已近三周，但尚未与中国王毅通电话。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 11:45:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3250609/china-willing-keep-touch-south-korea-first-phone-call-between-top-diplomats-wang-yi-cho-tae-yul?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>蚂蚁集团与上海建立战略合作伙伴关系，助力上海实现人工智能雄心</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3250566/ant-group-inks-strategic-partnership-shanghai-help-citys-ai-ambitions?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>蚂蚁集团与上海市政府达成合作伙伴关系，双方将深化在区块链和人工智能等领域的合作。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 11:00:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3250566/ant-group-inks-strategic-partnership-shanghai-help-citys-ai-ambitions?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>2023年中非贸易额达2820亿美元 但非洲贸易逆差扩大，大宗商品价格成关键因素</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3250552/china-africa-trade-hit-282-billion-2023-africas-trade-deficit-widens-commodity-prices-key-factor?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>由于中国与非洲主要伙伴——南非、安哥拉、尼日利亚、刚果民主共和国和埃及——主要是资源丰富的国家——的贸易下降，非洲的贸易逆差扩大至640亿美元。</description><pubDate